      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SMART STYLE (7) finished second last time (29.51) at this track after winning at his previous two outings. Form here sound including two wins. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. One of the contenders. IBROX MAVERICK (1) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at The Gardens but was a Grade 5 winner two back at this track. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Well placed here and should do much better. BLAZING RASO (6) has a strong record here with eight wins and two placings from 17 starts. Recorded a 9 length win (21.98) in a Mix 2/3 last time at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. TURN UP ACE (3) scored a scorching Maiden win in 22.73 last time. Can measure up again.",
